- The app will use python 3 as the main programming language
- The app will use discord.py as the main library
- The main API reference and documentation for discord.py can be found here https://discordpy.readthedocs.io/en/latest/api.html 
- The interaction API reference and documentation for discord.py can be found here https://discordpy.readthedocs.io/en/latest/interactions/api.html
- The bot command framework can be found here https://discordpy.readthedocs.io/en/latest/ext/commands/index.html
- The app will use SQLite as a database if it needs to store any data
- The commands will be located under /cogs folder and in subfolder if needed
- The utils will be located under /utils folder